      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and garlic have softened, add the <strong>chopped potato</strong>, <strong>broccoli stems</strong>, <strong>florets</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock </strong>to the pot</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook, covered, for 8-10 min or until everything is tender and cooked through</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1607609340261-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1607609340261-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1607609340261-x700.jpg",
