            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, blitz the soup with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>until smooth</p><p>Stir through your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> broccoli soup</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
